prodNameE: Vitros Immunodiagnostic Products Troponin I ES
ingredientsDesc:
Reagent Pack contains：
-100 coated wells (streptavidin, binds≧ 2 ng biotin/well).
-7.0 mL conjugate reagent (HRP-mouse monoclonal anti-cTnI, binds≧205 ng cTnI/mL) in buffer with bovine serum albumin and antimicrobial agent.
-7.0 mL biotinylated antibody reagent (biotin-mouse monoclonal anti-cTnI, binds≧205cTnI/mL) in buffer with horse serum, bovine gamma globulins, bovine serum albumin, and antimicrobial agent.
Calibrators contains：2 mL frozen, human cTnI in serum with antimicrobial agent；nominal values 0, 0.08, and 15 ng/mL (μg/L).
